  <title> Rational Functions section 3.6</title>
<p>
    Skills learned
</p>

<ul>
    <li>
        <p> Finding zero(s) of rational functions </p>
    </li>

    <li>
        <p> Finding asymptotes of rational functions </p>
    </li>

    <li>
